   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>This issue is just for keeping track of discussions about making the site
clearer to users, mainly in how the site can help the user achieve their goal,
e.g. "find something to help with" for potential contributors or "find people
who want to help" for project managers.

The discussion that sparked this is here:
<a href="http://irclogs.jackgrigg.com/irc.freenode.net/openhatch/2011-01-31#i_2523847">http://irclogs.jackgrigg.com/irc.freenode.net/openhatch/2011-01-31#i_2523847</a></pre>
